<tr id="L489"><td><a href="#L489">489</a></td><td>BRUNT [OC]:  It's not over, Quark.</td></tr>

<tr id="L490"><td><a href="#L490">490</a></td><td>QUARK:  Don't make me come in there after you.</td></tr>

